Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:21.45,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}不奮鬥的話就無法取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:23.07,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}去挑戰看看！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:26.24,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}快加油！快加油！這是你的時代！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:29.96,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}虎視眈眈地看清楚吧（全都是攻略法）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:33.48,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}提升經驗值然後變強吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:36.60,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}全部都提升吧（偶爾丟臉也正常）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:39.00,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}那要調成簡單模式？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:47.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}我要上（太棒啦）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:50.82,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}不是鬧著玩的吧 試煉接連不斷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:52.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}明顯做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.58,0:20:55.47,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}可能已經要逃跑了…（不可以）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.47,0:20:56.96,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}（重啟一下）（謝謝）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:21:00.26,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}不是鬧著玩喔 也不是那麼難做到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:05.01,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}不試試看怎麼知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:06.26,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}（開玩笑呢 笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.27,0:21:08.84,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}活著真的很難
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:12.64,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}但是也同樣美好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:16.47,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}是這樣 即使成為了大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:20.61,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}也能繼續升級吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:22.22,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}持續挑戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:25.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}不努力是你的撒嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:29.13,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}軟弱的內心也是（啪啪鞭打）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:32.44,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}用積極向上的對話來恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:35.92,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}定期存檔吧（休息也是必要的）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:38.28,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}那完全就是RPG嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:40.96,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}得好好做才行 得好好笑才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:44.75,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}如果手冊是這麼寫的的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.75,0:21:48.48,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}吸收其中技巧 調整為理想的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:50.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}重新製作一份吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.59,0:21:53.69,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}哇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.56,0:22:00.41,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}好！好！好！好！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.83,0:22:14.20,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}快加油！快加油！這是你的時代！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:17.60,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}（未來向你招手）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.83,0:22:22.77,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}在努力過後大聲歡笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:24.98,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}大家一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:26.56,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}再一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.56,0:22:29.87,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}快加油！快加油！這是你的時代！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.92,0:22:33.49,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}保持專注不要停！（大腦過熱進行時）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.49,0:22:36.81,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}橫掃大Boss然後通關
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.88,0:22:40.18,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}最後全通遊戲吧！（你將無人能敵）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:43.51,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}向著絕對的高分數前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.51,0:22:45.94,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}那就好好體會人生？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:50.97,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}快加油！快加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:54.40,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}快加油！快加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.04,0:22:57.98,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\an9\blur6\bord0\c&H000000&}快加油！快加油！
